---

<Layout
  title="Ignacio Amat Urbina - Full Stack Web Developer for Hire | PHP & Laravel Expert Barcelona"
  description="Hire a full stack web developer with +5 years experience in PHP, Laravel, Vue.js. Portfolio, resume and projects showcase. Based in Barcelona, Spain - Available for remote work worldwide. Custom web applications & high-performance websites."
>
  <main>
    <SectionContainer class="hero-section -mt-6 pt-2 pb-32 md:pt-4 md:pb-32 lg:py-32 lg:pb-40 min-h-[92vh] md:min-h-[95vh] lg:min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <!-- Availability Badge with pulse animation -->
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-8 mt-4 md:mt-0">
          <a
            href="https://www.ignacioamatweb.com"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block transition-transform hover:scale-105 group"
          >
            <Badge class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/50 text-green-800 dark:text-green-300 hover:bg-green-200 dark:hover:bg-green-800 transition-colors cursor-pointer relative overflow-hidden">
              <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                  <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-500 opacity-75"></span>
                  <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-600"></span>
                </span>
                Available for hire - View pricing
              </span>
            </Badge>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Heading with gradient animation -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight animate-fade-in">
          Hey, I'm <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-indigo-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent animate-gradient">Ignacio</span>
        </h1>

        <h2 class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4 font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <span class="font-semibold">+5 years of experience.</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-yellow-200">Full Stack Web Developer</span> from <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-200 font-bold">Barcelona, Spain.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-8 font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">Specialized in creating high-performance web apps and websites with modern technologies.</p>

        <!-- Tech Stack Pills with hover effects -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 mb-8">
          <span class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/50 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
            <PHPIcon class="w-4 h-4" />
            PHP
          </span>
          <span class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/50 text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
            <LaravelIcon class="w-4 h-4" />
            Laravel
          </span>
          <span class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/50 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
            <VueIcon class="w-4 h-4" />
            Vue.js
          </span>
          <span class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/50 text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
            <JavascriptIcon class="w-4 h-4" />
            JavaScript
